    </p>
    <a href="#pricing">
      <button class="px-8 py-3 bg-yellow-400 text-black rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-yellow-300 transition" data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-delay="400">
        Get Started Now
      </button>
    </a>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 bg-white text-black text-center" id="features">
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-10" data-aos="fade-up">What You‚Äôll Get</h2>
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-10 px-6">
